name: KUNKUN Coin
description: KUNKUN Coin is a meme coin based on a Chinese super start, Cai Xukun, AKA KUNKUN. KUNKUN is so popular in China that even pupils sing his songs! A lot of people love him while some are not, but all of them love the meme videos about him, which were viewed at least a billion times! We are a team of KUNKUN's fans, AKA iKun, who are willing to help KUNKUN to go global, letting more and more people know KUNKUN and enjoy the meme videos! Let's have FUN!
